title: Ambient Orchestral Moods Vol.1
description: A big collection of twenty-three original orchestral tracks with a AAA game soundtrack style and quality level. This collection was composed as a set and all fit together in style and sound.
longDescription:
Preview: https://soundcloud.com/sound-phenomenon/ambient-orchestral-moods-vol-2-sampler

A big collection of twenty-three original orchestral tracks with a AAA game soundtrack style and quality level. This collection was composed as a set and all fit together in style and sound.

23 tracks amounting to more than an hour of music:

1. Ancient Power (3:10)
2. Ashen Vista (2:30)
3. Auroroa Borealis (2:44)
4. Catacombs (3:00)
5. Cathedral Inner Sanctum (4:04)
6. Cathedral Yard (3:06)
7. Cemetary of Ash (2:13)
8. Choir of the Blue (2:41)
9. Cursed Ground (2:27)
10. Dark Beauty (2:10)
11. Dark Tower (2:40)
12. Dead Knights (3:10)
13. Journey Down (2:33)
14. Lake of Fire (2:46)
15. Magical View (2:06)
16. Poison Keep (3:21)
17. Ruined Fortress (1:53)
18. Sacrifices (5:13)
19. The High Wall (3:56)
20. The Shrine (2:32)
21. Through the Woods (2:40)
22. Tragic Hero (3:29)
23. Undead Town (2:30)
technicalDetails:
23 Tracks
23 cues
